{"tid":1783650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奧斯爾聲援新疆維族人　央視取消直播阿仙奴對曼城","createTime":"2019-12-15T04:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T05:02:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b143ed668a8bab4b1f3be9c0c9eb8a88181bab2","tid":1783650,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:56:12.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴球星、屬土耳其裔的奧斯爾（Mesut Ozil）前日（13日）在社交媒體發文，聲援被囚禁在新疆集中營的維吾爾族人，並批評為何其他穆斯林國家不出聲譴責新疆。雖然阿仙奴表明只是其個人觀點，但央視取消週一凌晨直播阿仙奴對曼城的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n根據央視體育微博公佈的最新周末節目表，中央電視台取消了原定於本週一凌晨 12 時 10 分直播阿仙奴及曼城的比賽。在12月13日，英超官方微博曾公佈，CCTV5將會直播阿仙奴及曼城的英超比賽。<br />\n<br />\n但央視體育微博公佈的直播節目時，CCTV5取消了對阿仙奴及曼城比賽的直播，這個時段改為錄播晚上 10 時的狼隊對熱刺的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n奧斯爾言論惹來中國網民批評，有人批評奧斯爾是支持恐怖主義活動，有網民則批評奧斯爾背叛中國球迷，亦有網民表明「國家面前無偶像，這種球員滾」。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴球會其後在微博發聲明，指奧斯爾在社交媒體上發阿布的言論，均為其個人觀點，阿仙奴作為一家足球俱樂部，一貫堅持不涉及政治的原則。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%B6%AD%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E9%98%BF%E4%BB%99%E5%A5%B4%E5%B0%8D%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%2597%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD%25E9%2598%25BF%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%25A5%25B4%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%259B%25BC%25E5%259F%258E%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=83a3546e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%2597%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD%25E9%2598%25BF%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%25A5%25B4%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%259B%25BC%25E5%259F%258E%2F&h=899d4557\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%B6%AD%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E9%98%BF%E4%BB%99%E5%A5%B4%E5%B0%8D%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E/</a>"},{"pid":"3ed19e5995555d60a6af9d7ce2660b989c662d5a","tid":1783650,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"Nba完到足球"},{"pid":"2af94d3d46a3cdff3a40a9cfa20f1a4e86ae0a53","tid":1783650,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"睇中超啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}